{
  "description": "A breathtaking night view of a cityscape illuminated with vibrant lights, dominated by a long bridge stretching across dark water. Above the city, fireworks explode in a brilliant display of reds, whites, and golds, creating a dramatic and festive atmosphere. The city skyline is densely packed with buildings, many lit up with orange and white lights. The bridge itself is also well-lit, showcasing its intricate structure and highlighting the traffic flowing across it. The dark water below reflects some of the city lights, adding depth to the scene. In the distance, a cluster of tall, brightly lit buildings stands out, possibly iconic landmarks. The overall scene conveys a sense of grandeur, celebration, and urban beauty.",
